// configuration file to integrate Spectral Film LUT
// (https://github.com/JanLohse/spectral_film_lut)
// into ART as an "external 3dLUT".
//
// Assumes that spectral_film_lut is installed in the Python interpreter
// available from the system PATH. If this is not the case
// (e.g. spectral_film_lut is installed in a virtual env), change the command
// line to point to the right Python interpreter
// (e.g. "/path/to/virtualenv/bin/python3" or similar)
//
// NOTE: when installing spectral_film_lut using `pip install -e .`,
// the following additional packages are needed (at least on my system):
//    matplotlib
//    networkx
//    opencv-python
// 
